OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, this most persistent and
OL,8,Fheaviest across the Southern
OL,9,FHighlands. Fresh to strong southerly
OL,10,Fwinds, easing later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FOvernight rain across the east
OL,13,Fslowly dying out by early afternoon.
OL,14,FOtherwise a dry day with some bright
OL,15,Fspells breaking through by afternoon
OL,16,Fin the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
